      "message": "It's always better if there's an approach that doesn't involve sleeping.  However, nothing obvious comes to mind here, so I guess adding NOSONAR would be ok.  Ordinarily, I'd use a latch to determine when something is done, but in this case, we're looking for the ABSENCE of something, so a latch wouldn't help.",
